text: Q'aysiri (Aymara q'aysa a kind of potato, (see: Papa, variedad alargada, de color blanco y morado y de tamaño regular) -(i)ri a suffix, also spelled Caysiri) is a mountain in the Andes of Bolivia, about high. It is situated in the Oruro Department, Sajama Province, at the border of the Curahuara de Carangas Municipality and the Turco Municipality. Q'aysiri lies north-east of the mountain Chilli Qhata. == References == Category:Mountains of Oruro Department
title: Q'aysiri
